I"L<div class="p">Six men of most enlightened fame,</div>
<div class="p">Six atheists, and all the same,</div>
<div class="p">Designed a dinner party, egg</div>
<div class="p">Of loneliness, in times of plague.</div>
<div class="p">Sir Seven could not so attend,</div>
<div class="p">King Northam would but condescend</div>
<div class="p">To let six gather for a home-</div>
<div class="p">Assemblage—so, Septet, shalom!</div>
<div class="p">They congregated, near and far,</div>
<div class="p">A timid, visored front of war.</div>
<div class="p">The ringer sounded, till within</div>
<div class="p">Resounded corresponding din:</div>
<div class="p">The door becks salmagundi troops;</div>
<div class="p">Instead desert the genial stoop</div>
<div class="p">These warriors of an honest faith.</div>
<div class="p">The door affords a fancied wraith?</div>
<div class="p">Nay, for a wimpled nose peeks forth,</div>
<div class="p">Forth from Sheol, the shadows' birth,</div>
<div class="p">Eccentric feathered fell bird, or</div>
<div class="p">The footman of dark Erebus' door.</div>
<div class="p">A cautious hand, as out of Hell,</div>
<div class="p">Or desperate hand of Jezebel,</div>
<div class="p">Defenestrated finery,</div>
<div class="p">And all consumed idolatry,</div>
<div class="p">Put out—a hijabbed head appeared,</div>
<div class="p">With disappointed eyes, and bleared,</div>
<div class="p">Enisled by coif and cursèd mask,</div>
<div class="p">That fitted closer than a basque.</div>
<div class="p">These rites announce a backward race,</div>
<div class="p">But not these Coventry of grace:</div>
<div class="p">Confession—raptured—ardent—great—</div>
<div class="p">Enthuses forth—what, Christian? late,</div>
<div class="p">Lewd?—unhygienic! Buckram rules</div>
<div class="p">Prevent indecent crimson jewels</div>
<div class="p">From tugging weather into lungs;</div>
<div class="p">But hear the throes of penance wrung</div>
<div class="p">From who embraced a sinner, wore</div>
<div class="p">The germs of social battle, tore</div>
<div class="p">A breath from diabolic mask,</div>
<div class="p">Shook bare hand, or shared naked flask!</div>
<div class="p">Pure absolution, bless his brow,</div>
<div class="p">That he may with a new-wrought vow</div>
<div class="p">Join fellow neophytes, fore'er</div>
<div class="p">Converted to their sorry prayer.</div>
<div class="p">He goes free of that unclean taint</div>
<div class="p">That made a leper of a saint,</div>
<div class="p">And doomed a superficial lad</div>
<div class="p">To the ill luck of being bad;</div>
<div class="p">Then see them issue through the door!</div>
<div class="p">What monkey antics could give more</div>
<div class="p">Of humor, pleasure, mock, or grief</div>
<div class="p">At such incongruous belief!</div>
<div class="p">The gate is narrow, they devise</div>
<div class="p">Ingenious ploys—lest any dies—</div>
<div class="p">To stay—lone pilgrims—with a part</div>
<div class="p">Of lost enjoyment (heart from heart)</div>
<div class="p">Their precious carcasses between,</div>
<div class="p">Like children on a trampoline.</div>
<div class="p">A bottleneck or passing doubt</div>
<div class="p">Of distance—horrors to their stout</div>
<div class="p">Redoubt despite one mutual sin—</div>
<div class="p">Too many angels on a pin—</div>
<div class="p">Is for the party passing dread,</div>
<div class="p">Constraining them to use their head.</div>
<div class="p">The last one files the doorway through;</div>
<div class="p">Let us contemn what then ensues—</div>
<div class="p">(They talk of reign on intimate</div>
<div class="p">Mere contact with a sobriquet,</div>
<div class="p">And proper manners with a Miss</div>
<div class="p">Or Mister—out of ambergris'</div>
<div class="p">Too potent charms, or ruby lips',</div>
<div class="p">Or fatal, fatal fingertips';</div>
<div class="p">Betimes men talked of youth apart</div>
<div class="p">From young corruption of a heart;</div>
<div class="p">These latter sages—one and all</div>
<div class="p">Great Puritans, austere withal—</div>
<div class="p">Mete strictures on the innocent</div>
<div class="p">Posthaste and temerarious bent</div>
<div class="p">Makes a youth touch a pretty hand—</div>
<div class="p">Good sir, forbear! that thing is banned!</div>
<div class="p">Lascivious youth! wouldst vitiate</div>
<div class="p">With an illicit finger straight</div>
<div class="p">The bare hand of a fellow wight,</div>
<div class="p">Or clutch it or by day or night?)—</div>
<div class="p">Preferring sight of plain wood door</div>
<div class="p">To such enlightened antics more.</div>
